sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    actor U as Pengguna
    participant B as Halaman Sub Menu
    participant C as MaterialController
    participant M as Material
    participant P as UserProgress

    U->>B: Mengakses sub menu materi
    B->>C: index()
    C->>M: getAllMaterials()
    M-->>C: daftar materi
    C->>P: getProgressByUser(userId)
    P-->>C: data progress user
    
    alt data progres user kosong
        C->>P: createProgress(userId, materialId, unlocked)
        P-->>C: progress created
    end
    
    Note over C: Menentukan status materi<br/>berdasarkan data progres
    
    C-->>B: render dengan status materi
    B-->>U: Menampilkan slider materi dengan status
